      <title>致命台风盖米导致菲律宾洪水泛滥，台湾停摆</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/taiwan-philippines-close-markets-as-typhoon-gaemi-floods-manila</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台风“盖米”在菲律宾造成至少四人死亡，迫使数十万人撤离，尽管台风正朝台湾移动，但首都马尼拉部分地区仍被洪水淹没。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/taiwan-philippines-close-markets-as-typhoon-gaemi-floods-manila</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 00:31:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
