    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行考虑将风险贷款调查中的需求减半至 70 亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/ecb-weighs-halving-demand-in-leverage-loan-probe-to-7-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行官员正在讨论要求银行增加约 70 亿欧元（76 亿美元）的杠杆贷款坏账拨备，约为最初估计的一半，此前该行对该业务的深入审查引发了银行的强烈反对。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/ecb-weighs-halving-demand-in-leverage-loan-probe-to-7-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 16:02:14 GMT</pubDate>
